data.title: Della Puspita
data.meta_description: Della Puspita is an Indonesian actor and presenter. Della started her career as female winner of the Malibu action photo competition in 1997. Subsequently, Della's face often graced various magazine covers. After that, soap opera offers came to him. Apart from that, she has also released a record album, "Kekasih Awal dan Akhir".

Della Puspita is an Indonesian actor and presenter. Della started her career as female winner of the Malibu action photo competition in 1997. Subsequently, Della's face often graced various magazine covers. After that, soap opera offers came to him. Apart from that, she has also released a record album, "Kekasih Awal dan Akhir".
